Lais Ribeiro is Ready for the World Cup in S Moda by Jonas Bresnan

Brazilian Babe—Brazil has some of the world’s hottest models, and Lais Ribeiro is living proof of that in the May 24th cover story from S Moda. Photographed by Jonas Bresnan of WM Artist Management, the Victoria’s Secret model takes on colorful looks from the spring collections with a sporty twist perfect for the upcoming World Cup next month. Fashion editor Chabela Garcia dresses Lais in designs from the likes of Alexander McQueen, Just Cavalli and Michael Kors for the glamorously sexy shoot. / Makeup by Fredrik Stambro, Hair by Miki, Manicure by Liang
